00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:17,080
Their hair is so shiny, I thought someone marinated their head in mucus.

562
00:24:17,080 --> 00:24:18,080
Time's up. It's your turn now.

563
00:24:18,640 --> 00:24:20,640
Time's up. It's your turn now.

564
00:24:21,600 --> 00:24:22,600
