579
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:49,960
Take a seat.

580
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:51,120
Oh, right.

581
00:24:51,120 --> 00:24:51,800
Okay.

582
00:24:51,800 --> 00:24:52,720
Please.

583
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:53,480
