591
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:13,960
How about a restaurant at my hotel?

592
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:15,200
Is it delicious?

593
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:17,600
Yes, it is. It's Italian.

594
00:25:17,600 --> 00:25:18,720
I meant...

595
00:25:18,720 --> 00:25:20,720
are you delicious?

596
00:25:22,800 --> 00:25:25,360
I'm gonna go get my stuff and we'll be ready to go.

597
00:25:25,360 --> 00:25:26,360
Of course.

598
00:25:37,160 --> 00:25:38,160
What's up, All-New?

599
00:25:38,160 --> 00:25:39,520
