608
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:58,200
I'll get there ASAP.

609
00:25:59,360 --> 00:26:00,280
Kree...

610
00:26:00,280 --> 00:26:01,280
Oh, Tid-Gift.

611
00:26:01,280 --> 00:26:02,360
