627
00:26:35,400 --> 00:26:36,480
What?

628
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:38,320
Go slide your little worm back in you own room.

629
00:26:38,320 --> 00:26:39,320
Farang!

630
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:43,000
What's sliding my little worm?

631
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:48,920
Cheers.

632
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:53,920
Guys, cheers.

633
00:26:55,600 --> 00:26:56,600
Cheers.

634
00:26:57,680 --> 00:27:01,680
Oh, dear. They're being copycats.

635
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:06,640
Just wait for my team to come, you won't survive.

636
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:13,560
Hey, that's Kree.

637
00:27:13,560 --> 00:27:14,600
Kree...

638
00:27:14,600 --> 00:27:16,600
So where are those people you're in a fight with?

639
00:27:20,840 --> 00:27:22,600
Hey, what are you doing?

640
00:27:22,600 --> 00:27:24,560
Oh, nothing.

641
00:27:24,560 --> 00:27:28,080
I'm just ready to punch someone.

642
00:27:28,080 --> 00:27:29,840
That's very good.

643
00:27:29,840 --> 00:27:32,240
Chai, who are you in a fight with?

644
00:27:32,240 --> 00:27:33,360
Gift!

645
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:36,360
The ultimate roasting device of Glamorous Airline.

646
00:27:36,360 --> 00:27:38,400
That table. Go on.

647
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:39,400
These four.

648
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:42,680
So these four?

649
00:27:42,680 --> 00:27:44,680
You think we're scared of you?

650
00:27:45,640 --> 00:27:47,920
Are you so free that you gotta pick up fights?

651
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:48,960
Look at you.

652
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:52,160
You're so old that you're about to die.

653
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:54,040
Can't you just sit and dine properly?

654
00:27:54,040 --> 00:27:54,960
What are you, gangsters?

655
00:27:54,960 --> 00:27:56,640
Some kind of Four Kings?

656
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:58,800
Please.

657
00:27:58,800 --> 00:27:59,640
There are four of you...

658
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:01,080
