662
00:28:08,120 --> 00:28:11,560
Honestly, tacky, tasteless, absolutely no class.

663
00:28:11,560 --> 00:28:14,120
If hitting the club is that much of a stuggle,

664
00:28:14,120 --> 00:28:16,440
maybe stay home and snack on watermelon and dried fish instead.

665
00:28:16,440 --> 00:28:18,040
Don't come here barking and howling like stray dogs.

666
00:28:18,040 --> 00:28:20,040
I swear I'll call the city inspectors on you.

667
00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:24,960
What? Why so quiet now? Weren't you all mouthy a minute ago?
Go on, keep talking.

668
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:26,240
Kree, All-New, go on.

669
00:28:26,240 --> 00:28:27,240
We're winning.

670
00:28:28,840 --> 00:28:31,840
Those two must be too polite to cuss you out, Madam.

671
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:35,400
Old hag!

672
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:37,720
Oh my god.

673
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:38,720
Too polite?

674
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:40,320
Let's go.

675
00:28:40,320 --> 00:28:41,320
