Hey, don't you think you must talk back?

677
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:52,480
Cheers, guys!

678
00:28:53,280 --> 00:28:54,280
Cheers!

679
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:55,400
Cheers!

680
00:28:56,320 --> 00:28:58,320
So how's that? They're quiet now.

681
00:29:00,240 --> 00:29:01,880
Why don't we go to other bars?

682
00:29:01,880 --> 00:29:04,480
Mr. Glam will be here soon.

683
00:29:04,480 --> 00:29:06,200
So I'd like to wait for him here.

684
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,640
Mr. Glam is coming?

685
00:29:07,640 --> 00:29:10,120
Oh, you're gonna get expensive gifts for sure.

686
00:29:10,120 --> 00:29:14,040
Wait, weren't you two in a fight over a guy?

687
00:29:14,040 --> 00:29:15,040
So where is David?

688
00:29:18,320 --> 00:29:21,120
He's gone. I told him to leave.

689
00:29:21,120 --> 00:29:24,040
I don't think we're gonna talk from now on.

690
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:31,440
Hey! Mr. Glam, the owner of their airline...

691
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:34,600
