692
00:29:34,600 --> 00:29:38,600
I'm so jealous. They really have a good boss.

693
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:43,480
Ano, why are you jealous?

694
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:47,200
Well, they got a caring boss. That's really kind.

695
00:29:47,200 --> 00:29:49,040
Madam Porn, our boss...

696
