697
00:29:51,320 --> 00:29:53,800
She only stays in her office.

698
00:29:53,800 --> 00:29:55,760
She never comes out of her room to meet people.

699
00:29:55,760 --> 00:29:59,160
Er...I think she might be busy.

700
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:01,160
No, she's not.

701
00:30:01,160 --> 00:30:04,160
She's too old to walk out of her office.

702
00:30:04,160 --> 00:30:07,440
That's true. She never knows...

703
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:11,440
