704
00:30:11,760 --> 00:30:15,240
From her lousy management.

705
00:30:15,240 --> 00:30:16,920
How is it lousy?

706
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:17,920
Well...

707
00:30:20,680 --> 00:30:22,680
Would you care for some tea or coffee...or water?

708
00:30:26,360 --> 00:30:28,360
What drinks would you...

709
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:32,240
Would you like some tea...?

710
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:36,400
We didn't have any passengers.

711
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:38,720
It's very lonely, we yawned all the time.

712
00:30:43,040 --> 00:30:44,880
And we faced crazy stuff each day.

713
00:30:45,640 --> 00:30:48,320
Please put it down.

714
00:30:48,320 --> 00:30:49,320
Please.

715
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:58,960
Hey, what's wrong with him?

716
00:30:58,960 --> 00:31:00,760
Did he pass out? Or is he drunk?

717
00:31:00,760 --> 00:31:02,840
No, he died.

718
00:31:02,840 --> 00:31:03,840
He died?

719
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:05,000
He died!

720
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:05,840
Someone died!

721
00:31:05,840 --> 00:31:06,400
Wait.

722
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:07,400
There's a dead body.

723
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:09,400
Wait, help me first.

724
00:31:12,480 --> 00:31:15,000
And with Glamorous Airline lauching,

725
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:17,000
