726
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:20,000
Is it that bad?

727
00:31:21,560 --> 00:31:26,560
But I believe that the owner of your airline is fighting.

728
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:30,400
Yeah, Madam Porn is fighting.

729
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:34,400
She's trying to copy Glamorous Airline's marketing plan.

730
00:31:38,840 --> 00:31:41,600
She decreased the ticket fee.

731
00:31:41,600 --> 00:31:43,600
But still, there were no passengers.

732
00:31:48,720 --> 00:31:52,720
