733
00:31:52,840 --> 00:31:55,560
But they were so terrible.

734
00:31:55,560 --> 00:31:57,960
Some wouldn't flush the toilet.

735
00:31:59,520 --> 00:32:02,000
Who pooped and didn't flush?

736
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:04,720
Who pooped? Did you poop?

737
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:06,920
Please go back and flush the toilet. Who pooped?

738
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:08,840
Some forgot their baby.

739
00:32:08,840 --> 00:32:11,160
Whose baby is this? Who forgot the baby?

740
00:32:11,160 --> 00:32:13,160
Oh, that's mine. I'll leave her to you for now.

741
00:32:15,600 --> 00:32:18,080
Some brought their own alcohol beverages to drink on board.

742
00:32:18,080 --> 00:32:20,560
Some got drunk and couldn't control themselves.

743
00:32:20,560 --> 00:32:24,560
Sometimes, they turned on karaoke and sang on the plane.

744
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:29,000
I wasn't sure if we're on the plane or on a tour bus.

745
00:32:29,120 --> 00:32:32,600
If this keeps happening, we're gonna be out of business.

746
00:32:32,600 --> 00:32:33,600
No way!

747
00:32:40,120 --> 00:32:42,120
We're not gonna let Glamorous have their way.

748
00:32:43,360 --> 00:32:43,840
We must fight!

749
00:32:44,360 --> 00:32:45,360
We must fight!

750
00:32:45,760 --> 00:32:46,400
We're not gonna lose!

751
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:47,400
We must not lose!

752
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:51,320
Why are you so into this?

753
00:32:51,320 --> 00:32:52,640
Well, we're on the same team now.

754
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:53,680
Oh.

755
00:32:53,680 --> 00:32:54,680
Okay.

756
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:57,400
We're on the same team now, right?

757
00:32:57,400 --> 00:32:58,400
Cheers!

758
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:01,400
Oh.

759
00:33:02,240 --> 00:33:04,840
I know a way to win for now.

760
00:33:04,840 --> 00:33:05,840
How so?

761
00:33:06,720 --> 00:33:07,720
Excuse me.

762
00:33:11,280 --> 00:33:12,600
Wow!

763
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:16,040
Oh my god.

764
00:33:16,040 --> 00:33:17,040
Surprise!

765
00:33:18,840 --> 00:33:20,840
It's my birthday, yeah, thank you.

766
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:24,760
This is the cake from a very famous place.

767
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:26,080
Very very famous.

768
00:33:26,080 --> 00:33:30,040
This is from Chef Ba's.

769
00:33:30,040 --> 00:33:31,520
Oh, that's so sweet of you.

770
00:33:31,520 --> 00:33:33,640
We got a birthday cake.

771
00:33:33,640 --> 00:33:35,960
Of course, we got a cake.

772
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:39,960
If there isn't a birthday cake, it wouldn't be a birthday. Oops!

773
00:33:41,760 --> 00:33:43,560
That's cute.

774
00:33:43,560 --> 00:33:45,560
That's a very cute birthday cake.

775
00:33:47,040 --> 00:33:49,520
Did anyone of you...

776
00:33:49,520 --> 00:33:51,520
