777
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:54,880
No?

778
00:33:55,680 --> 00:33:57,680
Do you want me to go buy you one from a convenience store?

779
00:33:59,320 --> 00:34:01,520
Buy me some sausages also.

780
00:34:01,520 --> 00:34:03,000
Are you nuts?

781
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,560
They only got a small piece of cake.

782
00:34:04,560 --> 00:34:05,560
It would be ridiculous.

783
00:34:07,720 --> 00:34:09,080
Would you like me to order one for you?

784
00:34:09,080 --> 00:34:12,440
It's too late. All the shops are closed.

785
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:15,440
Nevermind, guys. It's just a cake. Let it go.

786
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:22,360
Hello, Mr. Glam.

787
00:34:25,640 --> 00:34:26,640
Oh, you're here now?

788
00:34:30,040 --> 00:34:32,040
Oh, okay. Absolutely.

789
00:34:41,720 --> 00:34:44,600
Mr. Glam is not available now so he couldn't make it here.

790
00:34:44,600 --> 00:34:46,600
But he had me deliver the cake for you.

791
00:34:48,080 --> 00:34:50,080
That's alright. Thank you.

792
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:52,480
Wow, that's a big birthday cake!

793
00:34:52,480 --> 00:34:54,560
That's very pretty.

794
00:34:54,560 --> 00:34:55,560
Such an honor.

795
00:34:56,800 --> 00:34:59,680
It's a birthday, you're supposed to blow out candles on a cake,

796
00:34:59,680 --> 00:35:01,680
not on a Thai coconut pancake.

797
00:35:03,280 --> 00:35:06,080
Oh, my...if I'm not mistaken,

798
00:35:06,080 --> 00:35:09,240
this is the cake from a very famous place in France.

799
00:35:09,240 --> 00:35:13,040
They only have one shop in Asia and it's in Singapore.

800
00:35:13,040 --> 00:35:17,040
Mr. Glam is totally caring.

801
00:35:21,560 --> 00:35:23,560
I'll blow out the candles. They're melting into my cake.

802
00:35:25,720 --> 00:35:29,720
Happy birthday to you.

803
00:35:41,320 --> 00:35:42,320
That's fab.

804
00:35:43,880 --> 00:35:45,000
So what are we gonna do now?

805
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:48,720
Mr. Glam is not here. We got nothing.

806
00:35:48,720 --> 00:35:51,720
I must get something!

807
00:35:54,120 --> 00:35:55,200
What now, Madam?

808
00:35:55,200 --> 00:35:57,280
What are you doing?

809
00:35:57,280 --> 00:35:59,280
If I don't have it my way,

810
00:35:59,280 --> 00:36:01,160
I guess there will be some blood!

811
00:36:01,160 --> 00:36:03,160
Huh, a gun?

812
00:36:07,720 --> 00:36:10,360
Madam, please think straight.

813
00:36:10,360 --> 00:36:12,160
You'll end up in jail.

814
00:36:12,160 --> 00:36:14,400
