Our products are from Japan and Korea.

822
00:36:50,520 --> 00:36:52,400
100% authentic.

823
00:36:52,400 --> 00:36:54,960
Please have a look at Found and Found.

824
00:36:54,960 --> 00:36:58,160
You get the goods right away, no need to pre-order.

825
00:36:58,160 --> 00:37:00,120
That's fab, we don't have to wait for our turn to fly.

826
00:37:00,120 --> 00:37:04,120
What are we waiting for? Let's buy!

827
00:37:06,560 --> 00:37:08,600
Gift, wait for me!

828
00:37:08,600 --> 00:37:09,600
Hurry up!

829
00:37:09,600 --> 00:37:10,600
You ran so fast.

830
00:37:13,480 --> 00:37:14,520
It was very scary.

831
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:15,440
That's true.

832
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:16,560
We survived!

833
00:37:16,560 --> 00:37:16,920
Hey.

834
00:37:16,920 --> 00:37:17,480
